txt.en: You have turned in a stack of trophies for a modest reward suitable for a collector such as yourself.
Wanted: Broken wooden clubs from the Men and half-orcs in the areas around Echad Dúnann. Deliver the items to Tinúriel at Echad Dúnann.
'It is good to know that there are fewer defilers upon our lands. Thank you.'
'The enemies of the Free Peoples surround us. They are Men and half-orcs from the north and south. Fight them back and bring me their weapons, and I shall see you rewarded.'
Elves of Rivendell Task: Broken Wooden Clubs
Tinúriel at Echad Dúnann has requested that a collection of broken wooden clubs be delivered to her.
Deliver the broken wooden clubs to Tinúriel at Echad Dúnann in Eregion
You have accepted a task to deliver broken wooden clubs from the Men and half-orcs found near Echad Dúnann to the Elf-maid Tinúriel. Tinúriel can be found in Echad Dúnann.
Wanted: Broken wooden clubs from the Men and half-orcs in the areas around Echad Dúnann.
